com.radinfodesign.radspringbootgen.util

Class InputStringTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.radinfodesign.radspringbootgen.util.InputStringTree

  • public class InputStringTree
extends java.lang.Object
    Parse tree of input template txt file, composed of StringNodes having references to their immediate children, rolling up to a single Top node.
